Oct 8 (Reuters) - The following financial services industry appointments were announced on Wednesday. To inform us of other job changes, email moves@thomsonreuters.com.

COMMONWEALTH BANK OF AUSTRALIA (CBA) <CBA.AX> The country's largest bank in terms of market capitalization named Loretta Venten to run its loan markets syndications team. [ID:nL6N0S31IA]  BNP PARIBAS <BNPP.PA> The company appointed Sandrine Ferdane as country manager for Brazil and chief executive of its local operations there, subject to regulatory approval. [ID:nL6N0S31HD]  EDISON INVESTMENT RESEARCH